.DT
query_philosophy_needed
Disk World creator help
query_philosophy_needed

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_philosophy_needed -  This method returns the needed string of the philosophy.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string query_philosophy_needed(string name)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the name of the philosophy to get the needes string for
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the needed string for the philosophy.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/philosophies.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the needed string of the philosophy.  An example of the
return value from this is "the power of your faith".
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_philosphy_bonus(), query_philosphy_effect(), query_philosphy_type(), query_philosphy_argument()

.EP

